output.name: LoopCrateCycle
output.description: LoopCrateCycle is a B Corps-certified company dedicated to fostering a future without waste through innovative reuse and recycling solutions. Focused on community empowerment, environmental sustainability, and reducing landfill waste, it supports local nonprofits and promotes greener living. As a rapidly growing young company, LoopCrateCycle offers meaningful work opportunities with a strong emphasis on its core values of member-centric service, relentless pursuit of excellence, collaboration, and purpose-driven actions.

suboptimal.ground: A service that make it easy to reuse and recycle more by identifying recyclable and reusable items that the city doesn't collect, picking them up from our customers' doorsteps, and matching them with local partners that can use them sustainably. Our mission is to empower communities to waste less, and every success our team celebrates means more waste saved from the landfill and more valuable donations in the hands of local non-profits
